headline: U.S. Army Veteran Georgeo Pulikkathara Joins iMerit's Leadership as CIO & CISO
summary: iMerit, a leader in expert data for AI, today announced the appointment of Colonel Georgeo Xavier Pulikkathara, a distinguished U.S. Army Veteran, as Chief Information Officer and Chief Information Security Officer.

headline: ASC Advisors Launches Dedicated Digital Media Practice Led by Seasoned Industry Executive Ana Villarreal DuFlo
summary: ASC Advisors ("ASC" or the "Firm"), a strategic communications firm focused on the alternative investment management industry, today announced the expansion of its digital and social media capabilities with the launch of a dedicated Digital Media Practice. Ana Villarreal DuFlo, a seasoned financial services and communications agency executive with specialized expertise in digital strategy and execution, has joined the Firm to lead the practice as Senior Director, Head of Digital Strategy.
